.\n#oott https://t.co/8PIU8tnAEO", "time": "08:00", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119640, "views": 2932, "likes": 10, "replies": 0, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2063179473072082944", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2063179473072083285", "text": "If the crisis in the Middle East is resolved, oil markets could return to fundamentals in the second half of 2027, Igor Sechin, CEO of Russia's largest oil producer Rosneft, said on Saturday. #oott\nhttps://t.co/eGjHhkD7Vi", "time": "08:41", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119640, "views": 3293, "likes": 13, "replies": 0, "retweets": 4, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2063214355248786944", "url": "https://x.com/Rigzone/status/2063214355248787542", "text": "New agreements including pay increases averted a strike that had threatened to cut Norwegian oil and gas production by over 45,000 barrels of oil equivalent a day.\n\nhttps://t.co/3TpU6JqNn0\n\n#OOTT #strike #oilgas", "time": "11:00", "author": "Rigzone", "author_name": "Rigzone", "followers": 108802, "views": 842, "likes": 3, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2063238056862200064", "url": "https://x.com/ZmansEnrgyBrain/status/2063238056862199959", "text": "The Wrap (as alway, open to the public)\n#oil #natgas #oott \nhttps://t.co/UWmpvoMZVk https://t.co/gCX2J54dpv", "time": "12:34", "author": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "author_name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11776, "views": 1152, "likes": 7, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2063241594937987072", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2063241594937987388", "text": "Oil tanker owners fear market crash after Iran war drove record profits Shipowners ploughed windfall into new vessels and are braced for steep drop in rates if Strait of Hormuz reopens #oott  https://t.co/ndwzNZv7w3",